16:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-8-27 12:16am-10:16pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Bnofpzu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBnofpzu.png&h=2fa851a3&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/YmuflgT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYmuflgT.png&h=080699f9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(10)陳庭欣vs張沛樂(3)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"6565de8e1134ac1b96a542bdc3cc136095773bde","tid":375660,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:17:17.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱上半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363474\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363474</a><br />\n與此同時,LIHKG香港女神總會盃非聯賽參賽女神提名亦都已經展開,截止提名期為17年9月4日0時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9116045f97223a1df4e69142edadd829c35df9","tid":375660,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:21:59.000Z","msg":"黎喇黎喇投票啦"},{"pid":"28dfd9b81df02c7c1fe2bed1c2e0c9710b302962","